      "title": "'Even a dog does not respect Ranil's law'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Vasantha Mudalike, organizer of All University Students Union, said that not even a dog respects the Emergency Act implemented by Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "The appointment of Ranil as Acting President is not acceptable. He also said that people are deliberately fighting for Ranil to resign."
